{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_03_03",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 03 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1099.9999999999998,
          "startTime": 1.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 0.6666666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます～……あれ？\n二人とも、もう準備してたん？　いつもより早ない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning~… Huh?\nYou’re both already ready? You’re earlier than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 9.549999809265136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ……\nちょっと、すみれと二人で話したいことがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…\nI wanted to talk to Sumire for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.68333314259847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 13.88333314259847
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ～？\nうちも仲間に入れてや、仲間はずれは嫌や～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~?\nLet me join in too‚ I don’t wanna be left out~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.016666475931801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 19.449999809265137
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "仲間……\nなら、仲間として一つ聞くけれど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Comrades…\nThen I’ll ask you something as a comrade.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.016666475931807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 24.24999980926514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "昨日のパフォーマンスは、なんだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What was that performance yesterday?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.24999980926514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 26.699999856948857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっと……「なんだったの」っていうのは\nどのことなんやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… What do ya mean by “what was that”?\nwhich part?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.96666652361553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 32.66666652361553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "途中、急に私とパートを代わるよう言ってきたわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You suddenly told me to switch parts with you in the middle of the performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.66666652361553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 36.78467108408611
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、うちの考えた作戦やって\n普通にやるより絶対に会場が盛り上がる秘策",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told ya‚ it was the strategy I came up with.\nIt was a secret plan to definitely make the venue more exciting than if we did it normally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.81800441741943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 44.75133775075276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "結果的に会場は、うちらや瑠依ちゃんの\nパフォーマンスに釘付けになったやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a result‚ the audience was glued to\nour and Rui-chan’s performance‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.65133775075276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 50.43265317281086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "あんなことをしなくても\n優が前に出れば、会場を沸かすことは出来たはずよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You could’ve fired up the venue\njust by being in the front‚ Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9659865061442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 55.86278937657673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "買いかぶり過ぎやって\nそら、うちも実力はなかなかのもんやと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re overestimating me.\nSure‚ I think my skills are pretty good‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.17741308299203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 62.31113408406575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルにとって大事なんは、瑠依ちゃんが輝くことや\nファンのみんな……そしてうちも、それを望んでる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The important thing for TRINITYAiLE is for Rui-chan to shine.\nThat’s what all the fans… and I‚ want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.74446741739905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 71.97780075073238
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "分かった……それじゃあもう、単刀直入に言うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Then I’ll just be blunt.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.97780075073238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 76.3071884155273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "あんな舐めたバトルは、二度と許さない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t tolerate another half-hearted battle like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.3071884155273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 79.68213167190548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "……瑠依ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.68213167190548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 81.16213169097897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "優が私達のことを思って、作戦を立てたのは分かった\nでもあんなやり方は、私達が取るべきものじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that Yu came up with a plan because she was thinking of us.\nBut that’s not the way we should do things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.22879835764563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 89.04122486114498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "私達は三人で、トップアイドルを目指すって決めた\n長瀬麻奈を超えて、誰もが認めるトップアイドルに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We decided that the three of us would aim for the top together.\nTo become top idols who surpass Mana Nagase‚ and are recognized by everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.17455819447834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 97.47455819447833
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "そのためには、全てのバトルに全力で挑んで\n揺るぎない勝利を重ね続けないといけないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To do that‚ we have to give our all in every battle\nand keep accumulating solid victories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.10789152781162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 104.34122486114495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "別に、舐めてるつもりはないって\nこれは立派な演出やんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wasn’t trying to be half-hearted about it.\nThat was a great performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7078915278116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 110.60789152781159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとしたアウェー戦やのに圧勝したら\n相手の子達も、相手のファンも興ざめしてまう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we had won by a landslide in a bit of an away game‚\nthe other girls and their fans would’ve been disappointed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.541224861145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 117.40789152781166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ドラマチックに演出した方がかえって注目されるし\n相手もリスペクトしてくれるんやって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Making it dramatic would actually get us more attention‚\nand the other side would respect us more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.60789152781172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 124.60789152781172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "そういう演出は必要ないって言ってるの\n私達に必要なのは……常に全力で挑むことだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m saying we don’t need that kind of performance.\nThe only thing we need… is to always give our all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2078915278116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 132.64122486114493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
